I made this bank application with features to add, print, find, and delete a record. I used a linked list to store each record because there was a feature to delete records so I had to use a data structure that allowed me to easily delete and add records. To find records each record had an account number so the list was traversed until a matching account number was found. The list was saved each time the program ran and exited to a file.txt with all the details of each record and was read and wrote to each time the program starts and ends.
